In this study, we define three types of NPP. The first one is the actual NPPA, as calculated by the Carnegie Ames Stanford Approach (CASA) model39. The second is climate driven potential NPPP that is calculated by the Miami model40. The third is human activity driven NPPH41, which is the difference between NPPP and NPPA:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
